===Noun===
[[Category:Japanese nouns|てんわ']]
'''電話''' ([[でんわ]], [[denwa]])
# [[telephone]]
#*電話を[[掛ける]]<br>でんわをかける<Br>''denwa o kakeru''<br>to make a call<br><br>
