#*電話を[[切る]]<Br>でんわをきる<Br>''denwa o kiru''<br>to hang up<br><Br>
#*電話に[[出る]]<br>でんわにでる<br>''denwa ni deru''<Br>to answer the phone<Br><Br>
#*電話を[[引く]]<Br>でんわをひく<br>''denwa o hiku''<br>to install a telephone
